Nasa has selected a variety of companies to work on projects to create advanced space technologies . 
  The Vasimr engine is being developed by the Ad Astra Rocket company in Texas . 
  It uses plasma as a propellant and could get humans to Mars in just 39 days . 
  Other projects to be worked on include improved habitats for humans, and small satellites to explore deep space . 
  One of the projects is an engine that could reduce the journey to Mars from months to weeks . 
 